Title: Turning point<br>
Author: Hawkeye<br>
Rating: PG<br>
<br>
Andromeda belongs to some other lucky bastards; I don’t own any of them, even Trance. I mean, if I did, I’d have to keep her locked in my cupboard all day and only let her out in the evening!<br>
Oh, the song is (good riddance) Time of your life by Greenday. Its not mine either you know.<br>
<br>
………………………………………………………………………………………...<br>
<br>
