<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>So make the best of this test and don't ask why,<br>
It's not a question but a lesson learned in time.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Ever since she had swapped places with her younger self, she had known this day might come again. But she thought she had done enough already to stop it. She’d been wrong.<br>
<br>
